<P>
   (UNDATED) _ What will be the hot topic at the cocktail parties
during the annual meetings of the IMF and the World Bank in Prague?
Oil prices, the euro? Neither: the serious gossip will be about the
pay of top policymakers and in how much luxury they travelled to
the meeting. &QL;
