<P>
   (UNDATED) _ A military adage holds that a man under fire will
show the best or the worst side of his character. Judged by that
standard, Vojislav Kostunica, the stolid law professor who is
leading in the opinion polls in Yugoslavia's presidential race,
comes out rather well. Can he topple Serbian President Slobodan
Milosevic on Sunday? &QL;
