<P>
   &UR; KOSOVO OR SERBIA PROPER: WHICH ONE WILL BECOME A DEMOCRACY? &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; KOSOVO-MILOSEVIC-ECONOMIST &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   PRISTINA, KOSOVO _ Which place will become a decent democracy
first _ Kosovo or Serbia proper? The answer will greatly affect the
outcome of the unresolved battle between the Serbs, who hope the
breakaway province will remain within their orbit, at least
notionally, and Kosovo's ethnic-Albanian leaders, who demand
independence. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (TIMELY for this Sunday's election, Yugoslavia) &QL;
