   NYDIA-ROJAS (San Jose, Calif.) _ It wasn't even a week after her
appendectomy, but Nydia Rojas was ready to belt out her signature
ranchero songs for a PBS television show in Los Angeles. Still
tender from the surgery, the 20-year-old then flew to San Jose for
another concert at an outdoor theater with about 300 people
watching her every delicate move. No problem. By JUSTINO AGUILA.
</P>
