lie, but they often fail to tell the whole story. Take the image of
wide receiver Jerry Rice bellowing at coach Steve Mariucci during
Sunday's 41-24 49ers win in Dallas. What cameras didn't capture was
Rice going up to Mariucci shortly after his outburst and giving
Mariucci a hug. Rice, who appears embarrassed by the incident,
refused to discuss the matter. By KEVIN LYNCH.
</P>
