<P>
   ABORTION-DRUG _ Manufacturing, distribution and legal troubles
have bogged down the process, but the U.S. Food and Drug
Administration is scheduled to approve mifepristone (ru486) _ with
some potential restrictions _ by Sept. 30. How easy will it be to
obtain the drug in Atlanta, will some doctors refuse to prescribe
it, what will it cost, including costs of followup ultrasound, what
do local antiabortion groups plan to do, if anything, what does
that mean for abortion clinics? We'll answer those questions.
(Lore, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 30.
