<HEADER>
A5283 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u e BC-FILM-AFFAIR-REVIEW-HN     09-28 0316
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-FILM-AFFAIR-REVIEW-HNS </SLUG>
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
By ERIC HARRISON 
c. 2000 Houston Chronicle
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``It was a pornographic affair.'' That's how she describes it.
By that she means they met only for sex. Once or twice a week, she
says. Or was it less than that, the way her ex-lover remembers it.
</P>
<P>
   Time has passed. How much isn't clear. Memories play tricks.
</P>
<P>
   For its American release, the French film ``Une Liaison
Pornographique'' has been renamed. ``An Affair of Love'' first
seems a distortion, but it is appropriate. The relationship changed
over time.
</P>
<P>
   The couple passed through red corridors to reach their blue
hotel room. They met to commit a special act, never shown. Her
previous lovers would not consent to it. Neither he nor she will
describe it.
</P>
<P>
   They met through a magazine ad, he says; she says they met
online. He keeps the magazine, wrapped in plastic _ a souvenir.
</P>
<P>
   They talk to an unseen questioner. A filmmaker? Who or why isn't
told. Much is held in reserve. The characters go unnamed, for one
thing, to each other as well as to us.
</P>
<P>
   After their second meeting, they have dinner. Talk comes freely
with sex behind them and seduction not an issue.
</P>
<P>
   Things change. Emotions intrude. Fears.
</P>
<P>
   ``What if,'' she started one eventful night, ``What if we made
love?''
</P>
<P>
   Relationships cannot exist in such abstraction. They're drawn
outside. They look within.
</P>
<P>
   It lasted six months, the man recalls. She says three or four.
</P>
<P>
   At 80 minutes, this film has found the perfect length. That is
not to say that it is slight. Every tale is not a novel. Some
stories should be miniature in scope. &QL; 
 &QL; 
``An Affair of Love'' &QL; 
Starring: Nathalie Baye, Sergi Lopez &QL; 
Director: Frederic Fonteyne &QL; 
Screenwriter: Philippe Blasband &QL; 
Rating: R for some strong sexual content &QL; 
Running time: 80 min. &QL; 
Grade: B &QL;
</P>
<P>
   X X X END OF STORY
</P>
<P>
   $$$
</P>
