</P>
<P>
   --Latin America: ANA PENA in New York, 212-499-3333; fax,
212-499-3382. &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-09-28-00 1631EDT &QL; 
</TRAILER>
