``Gateway,'' opened this summer as the latest and most edgy of a
handful of internet portals for independent news and commentary on
everything from politics to health. Now, in the privacy of their
home, Arab teens can debate the pros and cons of premarital sex or
mixed-religion marriages. KAPLOW. photo of Al-Bawaba office.
