<P>
   Getting There From New York
</P>
<P>
   BY AIR: American Airlines, (800) 433-7300, has nonstop flights
to Vancouver from Kennedy Airport with round-trip tickets starting
at $514 for a 14-day advance purchase; the last-minute fare is
$900. TWA, (800) 221-2000, flies direct from Kennedy (stopping in
St. Louis, but no change of plane) and has connecting service from
Newark and La Guardia Airports; a round-trip ticket purchased seven
days in advance is $239.  &QL;
