<P>
   OPED/EDITORIAL
</P>
<P>
   EDITORIAL-JUSTICEDEPT _ Mr. Lee is the greatest spy since James
Bond? Then why did Justice Department let him walk? Something is
horribly wrong here. (Austin American-Statesman) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
