comes out ``sez nextonuthin.'' That's precisely what many
policy-makers want. Next to nothing. Clarification: Next to
nothing, they want full-throated advisories against it. It? You
know. It. Do I have to spell it out? S-E-X. (John Young is opinion
page editor of the Waco Tribune-Herald) MOVED.
