<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    AVIATION OFFICIALS REASSURE CONGRESS THEY ARE WORKING TO EASE
CONGESTION
 &HT;    DUPLICATION ALERT: Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial
categories
 &HT;    By KAVITA KUMAR
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ After a summer of frustrating delays, aviation
officials reassured members of Congress on Thursday they are
