u s BC-COX-OLY-DECATHLON0929     09-28 0051
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-COX-OLY-DECATHLON0929-ADVISORY </SLUG>

<TEXT>
<P>
   ATTN. EDS:
</P>
<P>
   CoxNet will not move the following story:
</P>
<P>
   OLY-DECATHLON
</P>
<P>
   Any questions, please call Diane Fall, CoxNet copy editor,
404-526-5456.
