<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-28 20:08 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5639 &Cx1f; tth-z
u e BC-FILM-GIRLFIGHT-SPI &LR;      09-28 0449
