<DOCNO> NYT20000928.0381 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-28 20:38 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5670 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f BC-ELIMINATE-OIL-BOS &LR;  &QC;      09-28 0029
